Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Soviet-China peace request
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wv6q
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 28 Mar 1982
Soviet president Brezhnev startles West by requesting peace talks with China. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.